    "content": "Ke$ha\r\nTik Tok\r\nTabbed by Salazard\r\n\r\nThis is a bass representation of the low synth. It's not exact but it's pretty much as \r\nas you can go on a normal bass.\r\n\r\nListen to track for timing. Play as smoothly as you can through the Chorus.\r\n\r\n\r\nSecond part of the verses\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------|\r\nD|-----------------|\r\nA|-1---1---1/3-3-5-|\r\nE|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nChorus\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------|\r\nD|---3---------5---7-9/19|\r\nA|-1---1---1/3---5-------|\r\nE|-----------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------|\r\nD|---3---------5---7-?/?-|\r\nA|-1---1---1/3---5-------|\r\nE|-----------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------|\r\nD|---3---------5---7-9/19|\r\nA|-1---1---1/3---5-------|\r\nE|-----------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------|\r\nD|--------------7---5----|\r\nA|-----5----3/5---3---3--|\r\nE|-3-1--3----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\nPretty much this repeated throughout.",
